> **I am aware that the guidelines say to not post content regarding suspended accounts but I'm kind of desperate at this point**

I logged in to my league of legends account yesterday after about two days of being offline and noticed that I was banned, however I did not receive a reform card or an email with information regarding my ban, even after relogging like the client said.  I've had an open support ticket since yesterday but have gotten nothing back yet, which I understand, these things can take time but I'm just very worried about my account.

Please help me! {{sticker:sg-janna}}
